{"tid":1402274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈，最有效嘅打狗方法","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:38:09.000Z","uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b74b71d6fc08c0af982f2d4f8d33bb9691033898","tid":1402274,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"今晚班狗竟然搞到去黃大仙，我非常相信類似於今晚咁嘅擾民行為，絕對會發生係其他各區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地好需要當區居民幫手打狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應該點打狗？</span><br />\n<br />\n其實好簡單，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">著背心踢拖嘅街坊look已經屌打班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n如果係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中年嘅阿叔/阿嬸，更加會有奇效！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n班狗專門搞鳩啲後生仔，如果係後生仔上前屌狗，十之八九會被狗屈襲警，或者被無理搜身。<br />\n反而啲中老年人聲大夾惡咁屌佢地，班狗係嗲都唔敢嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時我都想講，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所有上過前線發夢嘅手足，請盡量避免參與打狗行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班狗係會影相架，除非你好肯定自己除咗口罩眼罩之後，係第二個人，咁你先好上前打狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔係，都係留翻俾啲街坊做啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八月五號，全港三罷</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4618bd07930482583a4d56600badf9ac38009f","tid":1402274,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:02:47.000Z","msg":"要靠班叔叔阿姨掩護班後生仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c74d2770e05ff4344871a96623b26314a4890d9","tid":1402274,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"如果有狗嚟到你屋企附近，記得着背心踢拖落去打狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925a8f3338fac2f0c6a828f0e534fc791e6c5edd","tid":1402274,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae935ed9ca62431619e15d0a8b4124d719b6d86","tid":1402274,"uid":121048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:38:09.000Z","msg":"屌班狗已經癲咗，黃大仙都放彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}